<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٤ص١٠٧:</span> <span class="c3">{أَغْطَشَ}</span> وَ <span class="c3">{جَنَّ}</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span>: أَظْلَمَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{ضُحَاهَا}</span>: ضَوْءُهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
